:1410311,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"喺堵塞交通呢件事上面，大家要避免陷入群眾鬥群眾嘅陷阱，可能之後開始會有（犬儒/ 廢老/ 五毛）會吹風話示威者今次真係擾到民，鬧示威者喺度搞三搞四，但係請大家諗深一層，係啲乜嘢原因令到班示威者要咁樣做？<br />\n<br />\n歸根究底係政府冇回應五大訴求呀，警察開槍射頭，虐打手無寸鐵示威者，放任埋黑社會周街打人放煙花，警察仲要同黑社會有講有笑呀，催淚彈放題、開槍打頭、唔比食藥，已經有好幾個義士暈低咗未醒返，又有少女比黑警除曬底褲，將少女私處暴露喺眾人面前，如此劣行同當年日本皇軍有乜嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可，大家如果要指責，請向政府指責，因為政府冇回應到五大訴求，責任在於政府，而唔係好似呢幅漫畫「某文化」咁，反而指責為人民向奴隸主抗爭嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saa7Rku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsaa7Rku.png&h=58898183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"056272446c1c051757187260f993141486e73072","tid":1410311,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66pgXos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66pgXos.png&h=8ac89dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9q4mP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9q4mP7.png&h=efab8691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLFsjBR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLFsjBR.png&h=fb9bb273&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dj1o3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dj1o3w.png&h=59ad9c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"138a932159862f6d453d6d7fd55c8c089e9b789c","tid":1410311,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"你條友都ON9<br />\n亞叔我去左開壺水仙食點心<br />\n<br />\n射波咪算<br />\n又幫到後生又唔洗人迫人"},{"pid":"9b828c0870757623735102e661e2edd6722726b7","tid":1410311,"uid":105694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"ok我哋去碼頭等"},{"pid":"8a3fcbbdc641dde5ac2c1b8bb134ebcf627dd7ad","tid":1410311,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:49:37.000Z","msg":"咪暈低係條橋度呀